videos.description: DeMarcus Cousins gets the inbound pass and fades away to bank in a wild 3-point shot to beat the buzzer at the end of the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Cousins banks in incredible buzzer-beating fadeaway to end the 1st) 2021/06/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cousins banks in incredible buzzer-beating fadeaway to end the 1st

videos.description: Patrick Beverley crosses over Chris Paul, makes the tough layup and immediately goes at Paul with some trash talk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Beverley talks smack to CP3 after scoring on him) 2021/06/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Beverley talks smack to CP3 after scoring on him

videos.description: Devin Booker turns on the jets as he speeds to the basket and takes flight to flush down a powerful dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Booker races to the rack for emphatic throwdown) 2021/06/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Booker races to the rack for emphatic throwdown

videos.description: Devin Booker uses the screen and hurries to the basket to throw down an emphatic dunk to force a Clippers timeout.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Booker takes flight for another athletic slam) 2021/06/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Booker takes flight for another athletic slam

videos.description: Chris Paul crosses over Reggie Jackson and draws the contact as he knocks down a huge and-1 3-pointer from the top of the key.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (CP3 shakes Jackson to drain and-1 3-pointer) 2021/06/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: CP3 shakes Jackson to drain and-1 3-pointer

videos.description: Patrick Beverley loses his cool during a dead ball and is ejected from the game after he charges at Chris Paul and pushes him in the back.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Patrick Beverley gets ejected after pushing CP3 in the back) 2021/06/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Patrick Beverley gets ejected after pushing CP3 in the back

videos.description: After defeating the Clippers convincingly in Game 6 to win the Western Conference, Chris Paul races over to show love to Lil Wayne and bring him into the celebration.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (CP3 embraces Lil Wayne after defeating Clippers in Game 6) 2021/06/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: CP3 embraces Lil Wayne after defeating Clippers in Game 6

videos.description: Stephen A. Smith calls Chris Paul's Game 6 performance "the most special performance of his career" as the Suns advance to the NBA Finals.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA  Analysis (Stephen A., Wilbon marvel over CP3's Game 6 performance) 2021/6/30 ESHEET SC SVP

videos.headline: Stephen A., Wilbon marvel over CP3's Game 6 performance

videos.description: Chris Paul says Billy Crystal and the Clippers organization are like family as he celebrates advancing to the Finals with the Suns.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Chris Paul shouts out Billy Crystal as Suns make Finals) 2021/6/30

videos.headline: Chris Paul shouts out Billy Crystal as Suns make Finals

videos.description: Chris Paul drops 41 points with eight assists in a 130-103 Game 6 vs. the Clippers to advance to the NBA Finals.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (CP3 puts up 41 as Suns advance to first NBA Finals since 1993) 2021/06/30 ESHEET SVP SC

videos.headline: CP3 puts up 41 as Suns advance to first NBA Finals since 1993
